dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Prime meridians: Greenwich and Washington. "Entered according to Act of Congress in the year 1873 by Asher & Adams in the Office of the Librarian of Congress at Washington." In upper margin: 147-148. From: Asher & Adams' new commercial, topographical, and statistical atlas and gazetteer of the United States. New York : Asher & Adams, [c1874].
